parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to retract or lock
the seat belt buckle breaks or comes apart
the seat belt sticks or does not release
the seat belt does not function properly after recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ineffective recall repairs can lead to continued safety risks, as the original problem may not be fully addressed, putting occupants at risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt problem persists after recall repairs
the recall repair takes an excessive amount of time
the dealer claims the repair is complete but the problem remains.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil leaks can cause engine damage, overheating, and potentially lead to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Failure of the valve cover gasket can cause oil leaks, engine damage, and potentially lead to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil leaking from the valve cover area

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the fuel pressure regulator can cause engine performance issues, stalling, and potentially lead to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Failure of the motor mount can cause transmission shifting and vibration issues, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: unusual noises from the engine or transmission.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the muffler can cause exhaust leaks, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the transmission torque converter can cause the vehicle to buck and surge while driving, leading to a loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The transmission torque converter locks up
the vehicle bucks and surges while driving
the transmission downshifts on its own while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission mount can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to unexpected downshifting and loss of control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: the transmission downshifts on its own while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel assembly can cause the wheel to come off the axle while driving, leading to a loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The wheel comes off the axle while driving
